{"id":238786,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/07/维权网-武汉拆迁办断电逼迁，村民接电被暴打（/","date":"2012-07-09T14:01:09Z","modified":"2012-07-09T14:01:09Z","title":"维权网 | 武汉拆迁办断电逼迁，村民接电被暴打（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span><br /> </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span> </span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span></span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a>      </p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员方芳报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日</span><span>，武汉市桥口区长丰街长丰村</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>组的村民汪娥冤家因拒绝签订不合理的拆迁协议，通往家中的电线被拆迁办指使人给盗割，汪娥冤找来女婿汪勇给自己家接电，没想到窜出</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>多人不由分说将汪勇一顿暴打致重伤入院。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>     </span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>日</span><span>晚，汪娥冤家突然停电了，她出去一看邻居家里都有电，只有他们一家停电，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月酷暑难耐，赶紧找人查看原因，发现通往他们家的电表下端的电线被人盗割了，无奈汪娥冤只好告诉自己的小女婿汪勇，让他第二天下班之后过来给自己家把电线接上。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>点左右，汪勇下班后急忙来给岳母家接电，遭到拆迁办负责人的阻拦，说这一片已经被他们公司买下了，村民不能对房子的电线电表进行任何处理，此无理蛮横行为遭到围观村民的谴责，汪勇没听他不让接电的无理要求，继续为岳母家接电。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>没想到不一会拆迁办雇佣的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>多名凶神恶煞的打手蜂拥而至，不由分说过来就对汪勇一顿暴打，有人拿着砖头对着汪勇的头部猛拍，瘦弱的汪勇当即倒地起不来了，打手们像踢沙包一样将蜷缩在地的汪勇踢来踢去。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>    </span></span></div>\n<div><span>汪娥冤跪地苦苦哀求，请他们住手，打手们反而更加疯狂，对汪娥冤叫嚣道：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span><span>老不死的东西，你要是再敢动拆迁队的东西就连你都往死里打，今天先打他（汪勇）就不打你了。”</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span><span>　　</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>经普爱医院做的全身</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">CT</span><span>及</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">X</span><span>光检查，汪勇的鼻骨严重骨折、左边肋骨软组织受损、面部眉骨、人中皆被打裂，有多处很深的伤口，整个头面部严重青肿，全身各个部位出现了不同程度的淤青、淤血，牙齿被打落了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>颗，鲜血直流。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>    </span></span></div>\n<div><span>据了解，当地政府大搞“城中村改造”，要征收村民的房屋，因没有合理的补偿方案，汪娥冤等村民拒绝签订拆迁协议，村民们联合起来到上级部门上访并提出了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>项要求：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>  </span>1</span><span>、出示盖有省市政府公章的拆迁征地补偿公告的批文</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /><span>  </span>2</span><span>、依法召开听证会听取村民意见</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>  </span>3</span><span>、希望按照中央文件的要求以及唐良智市长所说的拆迁原则“先还建、后拆迁”</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>   </span>4</span><span>、希望按照</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2010</span><span>年中央</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>号文件提出农民宅基地确权的要求，按确权面积进行补偿。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>此举激怒了拆迁办的某些头头们，他们雇佣</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>多名社会闲散人员做打手，无辜挑衅村民惹起事端，伺机殴打村民，近日已有多位村民遭到拆拆办雇佣的打手的殴打。</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-DRjqWJFTOxY/T_rfIRMm6zI/AAAAAAAAJIw/zuvGeXc5atA/s1600/%E5%9B%BE1.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"183\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-DRjqWJFTOxY/T_rfIRMm6zI/AAAAAAAAJIw/zuvGeXc5atA/s320/%E5%9B%BE1.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span>汪娥冤家电表下被盗割断的电线口</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p></p>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-UlPQKi7TKpM/T_rfJ3pn1PI/AAAAAAAAJI4/OOxt3Qs-fM0/s1600/%E5%9B%BE2.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"304\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-UlPQKi7TKpM/T_rfJ3pn1PI/AAAAAAAAJI4/OOxt3Qs-fM0/s320/%E5%9B%BE2.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span>被打伤的汪勇</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span><br /></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span><span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<p><span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span><span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /><br style=\"\"/><br style=\"\"/></span></div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-4084031341461601433?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/07/1515de54E59BBE1.jpg-150x150.jpg\" /></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18269,20534],"tags":[16910,19196]}